{"tid":606878,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"80後情侶辭筍工瞓身兼職　唔「上車」買船住","createTime":"2018-03-27T00:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T09:40:40.000Z","uid":81228,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"350b7b19651ffa680d2b4522acc2b506fbcb62dc","tid":606878,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:00:30.000Z","msg":"今時今日，香港樓價癲得嚇人，若沒「父幹」，任你死慳死抵，不吃不喝N年也未必可成功上車，看似荒謬，但仍有不少年輕人以此為終極目標。有80後情侶不甘做羊群，不買樓，三年前裸辭出走環遊世界一年後，回港一擲十多萬買下一艘舊遊艇，以此為家，就算要日打三份兼職養船，為船而活，也覺無憾。<br />\n<br />\n今年32歲的羅家健（Rex）和葉翠霞（Sarah），原本是在中環商廈返工的白領，在長洲長大、性格坐不定的Rex，工作10年後決定出走到澳洲和愛爾蘭工作假期；鍾意旅行、留港繼續打工的Sarah，不想再面對辦公室政治，3年前也毅然辭去高薪厚職，陪Rex環遊世界，二人花一年時間環遊了38個國家，回港後，就算有不少獵頭公司叫他們返工，都一一拒絕，最後選擇在長洲買一艘43呎長的三手遊艇居住，兼全職打理，算是圓了Rex自小的海上生活夢。「樓價太癲，點解要用癲價去做自己唔鍾意嘅事？我哋<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180327/large/27fj501p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180327%2Flarge%2F27fj501p.jpg&h=24bd5523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRex和Sarah不甘做羊群，不買樓，年多前買下一艘43呎長的舊遊艇，以此為家。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180327/large/27fj504p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180327%2Flarge%2F27fj504p.jpg&h=6e2a106c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這個小小的家，是靠二人一手一腳打做出來的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180327/large/27fj505p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180327%2Flarge%2F27fj505p.jpg&h=7951042f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180327/large/27fj508p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180327%2Flarge%2F27fj508p.jpg&h=881ee378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他們的家裝潢簡單，睡房只得一張梳化床。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180327/large/27fj509p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180327%2Flarge%2F27fj509p.jpg&h=9f65f73b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朋友親手為他們的「飯枱」畫了一幅世界地圖，對曾環遊世界的二人別具意義。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180327/large/27fj502p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180327%2Flarge%2F27fj502p.jpg&h=1d3069e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二人不時會去長洲的船廠和機器廠找工人傾偈偷師。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20180327/20343591?_ga=2.47888551.1099540509.1522107110-1775759209.1522107110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180327%2F20343591%3F_ga%3D2.47888551.1099540509.1522107110-1775759209.1522107110&d=f%2BmPlfixWRiD26j9HppfkYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=2db2d923\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180327%2F20343591%3F_ga%3D2.47888551.1099540509.1522107110-1775759209.1522107110&h=04c6c1e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20180327/20343591?_ga=2.47888551.1099540509.1522107110-1775759209.1522107110</a>"},{"pid":"cdc0408d093c8bf349d60ab09b9ee7ead27e8f12","tid":606878,"uid":25689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"船p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1e3290b94623b9b81750ed23cb6ae654c29a07","tid":606878,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T07:43:54.000Z","msg":"係船到爆房, 會唔會好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf3810b5d8e99dfbabb3b0860